    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the air conditioning, while functional, takes a few minutes to get cold. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that gets the job done without any frills.",
      "price": 19000.0,
