    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional find! This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and feeling as pristine as the day it was first driven. With its flawless exterior and showroom-quality interior, it offers a rare opportunity to own a car that has been meticulously preserved. You won't find a single blemish on this beauty\u2014it's ready for its next proud owner!",
