    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. There are visible scuffs and minor dings on the exterior, and the interior shows some wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it may require some routine maintenance like new brake pads or a tune-up in the near future. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a showroom model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
